    "title": "Israeli drone strike hits southern Lebanon day after security deal",
    "description": "BEIRUT: Israel ​struck southern Lebanon on Saturday, a day after the two countries signed a US-brokered security arrangement aimed at easing ‌tensions along ‌their ​border after ‌months ⁠of ​hostilities. Lebanon’s state news ⁠agency said an Israeli drone struck in Nabatieh Al-Fawqa, which lies outside a security zone ⁠shown on a map ‌published ‌by Israel ​of an ‌expanded zone",
